  "_doc": [
    "Run-registry config for the Phase-3 analysis pipeline. The author edits this",
    "as runs finish: set 'run_dir' to the on-disk run directory name and flip",
    "'status' to 'scored'. The loader drives everything off this file; a model with",
    "no metrics on disk (pending/in_progress, or run_dir blank) is skipped with a",
    "logged note, never an error. Order is reporting order: frontier reference",
    "points first (one flagship per lab), then the Qwen open-ladder, with the MoE",
    "ceiling last. Sonnet is supplementary (off the main 7-model panel by default).",
    "Per-model fields: id (stable key), display (table label), run_dir (the shared",
    "name under data/{csr,element_f1,relationship_f1,chrf}/<run_dir>/ and",
    "data/runs/<run_dir>/), status (scored|in_progress|pending), lab, arm",
    "(frontier|qwen), family (dense|moe), params_total_b / params_active_b",
    "(billions; null where the lab does not disclose), supplementary (bool)."
